ActPrivacy Act
PrecisAppointment of CHANTAL BERNIER of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Privacy Commissioner on an interim basis, to hold office during good behaviour for a maximum term of six months or until such time as a Privacy Commissioner is appointed, effective December 3, 2013.
